---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { getLocaleFromUrl, t, localizedPath } from '@/lib/i18n';

const locale = getLocaleFromUrl(Astro.url);
const dict = t(locale);
const isZh = locale === 'zh-TW';
---

<BaseLayout title={`About · Runpeng Ma`}>
  <section class="container-page py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-aqua-600 reveal">
        {dict.nav.about}
      </p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-bold text-ink sm:text-5xl reveal">
        {isZh ? '關於我' : 'About Me'}
      </h1>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink-muted sm:text-lg reveal">
        {isZh ? (
          <>
            <p>
              我是 <strong class="text-ink">馬潤芃（Runpeng Ma）</strong>，2025 年於 UNSW Sydney 完成電子工程碩士學位，本科畢業於上海交通大學<strong class="text-ink">微電子科學與工程</strong>學系。研究方向橫跨 <strong class="text-ink">MEMS 物理建模</strong>與 <strong class="text-ink">CMOS 類比 / 混訊 IC 設計</strong>。
            </p>
            <p>
              碩士論文設計了一款電子驅動 MEMS 光開關，提出用 SiO₂ 蛇形彈簧取代傳統 torsion 結構，搭配分裂式底電極差動驅動方案，淨扭矩放大 4 倍。完整建立了電-機耦合解析模型，並在 COMSOL Multiphysics 上完成靜態與動態雙模擬，理論與模擬吻合度達 99%。
            </p>
            <p>
              在類比 IC 設計領域，我使用 Cadence Virtuoso 與 FreePDK 45 nm 製程，獨立或與隊友合作完成兩個專案：rail-to-rail 差動比較器（0.9 V 電源）、LS-Buffer 兩階運算放大器（電壓位準轉換）。兩者都經過 Monte Carlo 與 Corner 驗證流程。
            </p>
            <p>
              我喜歡把<strong class="text-ink">物理直覺</strong>與<strong class="text-ink">電路層級設計</strong>連在一起。寫公式時想著電晶體在做什麼；佈局時想著電場怎麼分布。MEMS 教會我從元件到系統的完整鏈路；類比 IC 訓練我在電晶體層級做精細決定。
            </p>
            <p>
              目前在台灣尋求<strong class="text-ink">類比 / 混訊 IC 工程師、MEMS 工程師</strong>相關職缺。
            </p>
          </>
        ) : (
          <>
            <p>
              I'm <strong class="text-ink">Runpeng Ma</strong>. I completed my Master of Engineering in Electrical Engineering at UNSW Sydney in 2025, with a B.Eng in <strong class="text-ink">Microelectronic Science and Engineering</strong> from Shanghai Jiao Tong University. My work spans <strong class="text-ink">MEMS physical modeling</strong> and <strong class="text-ink">CMOS analog / mixed-signal IC design</strong>.
            </p>
            <p>
              For my master's thesis, I designed an electrostatically driven MEMS optical switch. I replaced the traditional torsion structure with SiO₂ serpentine springs and adopted a split-bottom-electrode differential drive — amplifying net torque by 4×. I built a complete electromechanical coupled model and validated it in COMSOL Multiphysics with both static and dynamic simulations, achieving 99% theory-vs-simulation agreement.
            </p>
            <p>
              In analog IC design, using Cadence Virtuoso on FreePDK 45 nm, I have completed two projects (solo and team): a rail-to-rail differential comparator at 0.9 V supply, and an LS-Buffer two-stage op-amp for voltage level shifting. Both went through Monte Carlo and corner-analysis verification flows.
            </p>
            <p>
              I enjoy connecting <strong class="text-ink">physical intuition</strong> with <strong class="text-ink">circuit-level design</strong>. When deriving equations I'm thinking about what the transistor is doing; when laying out, I'm thinking about how the field distributes. MEMS gave me end-to-end thinking from device to system; analog IC trained me to make fine-grained decisions at transistor level.
            </p>
            <p>
              I'm currently seeking <strong class="text-ink">analog / mixed-signal IC engineer or MEMS engineer</strong> roles in Taiwan.
            </p>
          </>
        )}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-aqua-200 bg-white p-6 reveal">
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-aqua-600">{dict.education.unsw.period}</p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 font-display text-lg font-semibold text-ink">{dict.education.unsw.school}</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-muted">{dict.education.unsw.degree}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-aqua-100 bg-aqua-50/30 p-6 reveal">
          <p class="font-mono text-xs text-aqua-600">{dict.education.sjtu.period}</p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 font-display text-lg font-semibold text-ink">{dict.education.sjtu.school}</h3>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-ink-muted">{dict.education.sjtu.degree}</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-3 reveal">
        <a href={localizedPath(locale, '/resume')} class="btn-primary">
          {dict.contact.downloadResume}
        </a>
        <a href={localizedPath(locale, '/#projects')} class="btn-ghost">
          {isZh ? '回首頁看專案' : 'See Projects'}
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
